<!-- agent-model-optimizer:start -->

## Model routing

Route work by task complexity. Match your model selection in Windsurf to these tiers:

| Task | Tier | Windsurf guidance |
|------|------|-------------------|
| Codebase search, file discovery | fast | Use Cascade Fast / lightweight mode |
| Shell, git, CI scripts | fast | Use Cascade Fast |
| Implementation, refactoring | balanced | Default coding model |
| Tests | balanced | Default coding model |
| Code review, debugging | balanced-thinking | Standard model; allow reasoning time |
| Security, architecture | high-thinking | Most capable model available |

### Delegation habits

- Do exploration and search in a **fast** tier before reading entire files
- Run terminal work without upgrading model unless errors need deep analysis
- Use **high-thinking** only for security review, architecture, and complex migrations
- Do not use the most capable model for grep, glob, or formatting tasks

<!-- agent-model-optimizer:end -->
